    <tags>crawler web scraping spider rust</tags>
    <summary>Production-ready web crawler capable of handling billions of URLs</summary>
    <description>
Argus is a production-ready web crawler built in Rust, designed to handle billions of URLs efficiently.
It features distributed crawling, content deduplication, JavaScript rendering support, and a Redis-based URL frontier.

Key features:
- High-performance async crawling
- Distributed architecture with Redis
- Content deduplication with Simhash
- JavaScript rendering support
- Robots.txt compliance
- Configurable politeness policies
- Multiple storage backends

This package installs the argus-crawler command-line tool.
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>Initial release v0.1.0</releaseNotes>
